commitResults.messageBody:
Implement a skeletal version of Duke that starts by greeting the user,
simply echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types bye.

Change indentation from one space to one tab.

Add the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and
display them back to the user when requested.
